<s> Is it possible to use Tidy to clean some html documents so that it automatically removes....  </s>
<s> Any javascript Any styles and class references Any comments?  </s>
<s> Cheers, Julian Voelcker The Virtual World (UK) Limited Cirencester, United Kingdom  </s>
<s> Comments using the --hide-comments yes configuration option; there is no such option for scripts, styles or class attributes, you must either post-process the Tidy result or write your own Tidy application based on the library.  </s>
<s> I would use dsssl and openjade.  </s>
<s> This is a variation of the identity transformation with elimination of certain elements or attributes.  </s>
